<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="mn">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>G-Trader Pro — AI Signal Robot</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rajdhani:wght@500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg:       #060810;
  --s1:       #0b0f1e;
  --s2:       #0f1628;
  --border:   #1a2540;
  --green:    #00f0a0;
  --red:      #ff3060;
  --blue:     #3d8fff;
  --gold:     #ffb800;
  --purple:   #a259ff;
  --cyan:     #00d4ff;
  --text:     #c0d4ee;
  --muted:    #3a5278;
  --font:     'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
  --mono:     'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
}

/* ── LIGHT MODE ── */
body.light {
  --bg:     #f0f4f8;
  --s1:     #ffffff;
  --s2:     #e8eef5;
  --border: #d0dbe8;
  --text:   #1a2a3a;
  --muted:  #5a7a98;
  --green:  #00b87a;
  --blue:   #2266cc;
  --red:    #cc2244;
  --gold:   #cc8800;
}
body.light header {
  background: rgba(240,244,248,.95);
}
body.light .brand-name h1 {
  color: #0a1a2a !important;
}
body.light .brand-name p {
  color: #5a7a98 !important;
}
body.light .drop-title {
  color: #0a1a2a !important;
}
body.light .signal-big {
  filter: brightness(0.85);
}
body.light .badge-live {
  background: rgba(0,180,120,.12);
  border-color: rgba(0,180,120,.3);
}
body.light::before {
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 20% 10%, rgba(0,180,120,.06) 0%, transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 30% at 80% 90%, rgba(61,143,255,.05) 0%, transparent 60%),
    linear-gradient(rgba(0,180,120,.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,180,120,.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: auto, auto, 44px 44px, 44px 44px;
}

body.light .btn-analyze {
  color: #fff;
}
body.light .signal-hero {
  box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}

*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}

body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: var(--font);
  min-height: 100vh;
  font-size: 15px;
}

/* Animated background */
body::before {
  content:'';
  position:fixed;inset:0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 20% 10%, rgba(0,240,160,.04) 0%, transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 30% at 80% 90%, rgba(61,143,255,.04) 0%, transparent 60%),
    linear-gradient(rgba(0,240,160,.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,240,160,.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: auto, auto, 44px 44px, 44px 44px;
  pointer-events:none;z-index:0;
}

/* ── HEADER ── */
header {
  position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;
  background: rgba(6,8,16,.85);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 0 28px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  height: 64px;
}

.brand { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; }

.brand-logo {
  width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:10px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green), var(--blue));
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-family:var(--font);font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#000;
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,240,160,.4), 0 0 60px rgba(0,240,160,.1);
  position:relative;
}
.brand-logo::after {
  content:'';position:absolute;inset:-3px;border-radius:13px;
  border:1px solid rgba(0,240,160,.3);
}

.brand-name { line-height:1.1; }
.brand-name h1 {
  font-family:var(--font);font-size:22px;font-weight:700;
  color:#fff;letter-spacing:4px;
}
.brand-name p { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:3px;margin-top:2px; }

.header-right { display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px; }

.badge {
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;
  padding:6px 14px;border-radius:999px;
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;
}
.badge-live { background:rgba(0,240,160,.08);border:1px solid rgba(0,240,160,.2);color:var(--green); }
.badge-dot  { width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);animation:blink 2s infinite; }

.theme-icon { font-size:22px;cursor:pointer; }

/* ── MAIN ── */
main { position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:28px 20px 80px; }

/* ── STRATEGY PILLS ── */
.strategy-grid {
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:8px;margin-bottom:24px;
}

.s-card {
  padding:12px;border-radius:12px;
  background:var(--s1);border:1px solid var(--border);
  text-align:center;transition:all .3s;
}
.s-card:hover { border-color:var(--green);background:rgba(0,240,160,.04); }
.s-card .s-icon { font-size:20px;margin-bottom:5px; }
.s-card .s-title { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:3px; }
.s-card .s-name  { font-weight:600;font-size:13px;color:var(--text); }

/* ── SECTION TITLE ── */
.section-title {
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);
  letter-spacing:4px;margin-bottom:10px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
}
.section-title::after { content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border); }

/* ── API KEY ── */
.api-box {
  background:var(--s1);border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:14px;padding:18px;margin-bottom:20px;
}
.api-box label { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:4px;display:block;margin-bottom:10px; }
.api-input {
  width:100%;background:var(--bg);
  border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;
  padding:12px 16px;color:var(--text);
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;outline:none;
  transition:border-color .2s;
}
.api-input:focus { border-color:var(--green); }
.api-hint { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:8px; }
.api-hint a { color:var(--blue);text-decoration:none; }
.api-hint a:hover { text-decoration:underline; }

/* ── DROP ZONE ── */
#drop-zone {
  border:2px dashed var(--border);border-radius:16px;
  cursor:pointer;background:var(--s1);
  transition:all .3s;margin-bottom:14px;overflow:hidden;
  min-height:140px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
}
#drop-zone:hover,#drop-zone.drag {
  border-color:var(--green);
  background:rgba(0,240,160,.03);
  box-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(0,240,160,.06);
}
#drop-zone.has-image { min-height:auto;border-style:solid;border-color:var(--border); }

.drop-inner { text-align:center;padding:40px 20px; }
.drop-icon  { font-size:40px;margin-bottom:12px;filter:grayscale(.4); }
.drop-title { font-family:var(--font);font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:5px; }
.drop-sub   { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--muted); }

#preview { width:100%;display:block;border-radius:14px; }
#file-input { display:none; }

/* ── BUTTONS ── */
.btn-row { display:flex;gap:10px;margin-bottom:16px; }

.btn-analyze {
  flex:1;padding:15px;border:none;border-radius:12px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green) 0%, var(--blue) 100%);
  color:#000;font-family:var(--font);font-size:16px;font-weight:700;
  letter-spacing:2px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s;
  box-shadow:0 6px 30px rgba(0,240,160,.25);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:10px;
}
.btn-analyze:hover:not(:disabled) {
  transform:translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow:0 10px 40px rgba(0,240,160,.35);
}
.btn-analyze:disabled {
  background:var(--s2);color:var(--muted);cursor:default;
  transform:none;box-shadow:none;
}

.btn-clear {
  padding:15px 20px;border-radius:12px;
  border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--s1);
  color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;font-size:18px;
  transition:all .2s;
}
.btn-clear:hover { border-color:var(--red);color:var(--red); }

/* ── SPINNER ── */
.spinner {
  width:17px;height:17px;
  border:2px solid rgba(0,0,0,.3);
  border-top-color:#000;
  border-radius:50%;
  animation:spin .7s linear infinite;
}

/* ── ERROR ── */
.error-box {
  background:rgba(255,48,96,.07);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,48,96,.25);
  border-radius:12px;padding:14px 16px;
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:#ff7090;
  word-break:break-all;margin-bottom:16px;
  line-height:1.7;
}

/* ── RESULT CARDS ── */
.result { display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;animation:fadeUp .5s ease; }

/* Signal hero */
.signal-hero {
  border-radius:16px;padding:24px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.signal-hero::before {
  content:'';position:absolute;
  top:-60px;right:-60px;width:200px;height:200px;
  border-radius:50%;opacity:.06;
  background:radial-gradient(circle, currentColor 0%, transparent 70%);
}

.signal-hero-top {
  display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;
  margin-bottom:18px;
}

.signal-big {
  font-family:var(--font);font-size:48px;font-weight:700;
  line-height:1;letter-spacing:3px;
}
.signal-sub { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:8px; }

.conf-block { text-align:right; }
.conf-num   { font-family:var(--font);font-size:44px;font-weight:700;line-height:1; }
.conf-label { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:4px; }
.rr-label   { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px; }

.prog-track { background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border-radius:999px;height:4px;overflow:hidden; }
.prog-fill  { height:100%;border-radius:999px;transition:width 1.3s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1); }

/* Card */
.card {
  background:var(--s1);border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;
}
.card-head {
  padding:12px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:4px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
}

/* Analysis tabs */
.analysis-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:0; }
.analysis-col  { padding:16px; }
.analysis-col:first-child { border-right:1px solid var(--border); }
.analysis-label { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:10px; }

.indicator-row {
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.04);
}
.indicator-row:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
.ind-name { font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text); }
.ind-val  { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:6px; }
.ind-ok   { background:rgba(0,240,160,.12);color:var(--green); }
.ind-bad  { background:rgba(255,48,96,.1);color:var(--red); }
.ind-mid  { background:rgba(255,184,0,.1);color:var(--gold); }

/* Levels */
.levels-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:var(--border); }
.level-cell  { background:var(--s1);padding:14px 12px; }
.level-lbl   { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:8px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:5px; }
.level-val   { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:14px;font-weight:700; }

/* Reasoning */
.reasoning { padding:16px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#8ab4d0; }

/* Telegram */
.tg-body {
  padding:14px 16px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;
  line-height:1.9;color:var(--muted);white-space:pre-wrap;
  word-break:break-word;max-height:240px;overflow-y:auto;
}

.btn-copy {
  padding:5px 14px;border:none;border-radius:7px;
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;
  cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;
  background:rgba(61,143,255,.15);color:var(--blue);
}
.btn-copy.copied { background:rgba(0,240,160,.18);color:var(--green); }

/* Dow Theory visual */
.dow-visual {
  padding:16px;display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;
}
.dow-tag {
  padding:5px 12px;border-radius:999px;
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;
  letter-spacing:1px;
}
.dow-bull { background:rgba(0,240,160,.12);color:var(--green);border:1px solid rgba(0,240,160,.25); }
.dow-bear { background:rgba(255,48,96,.1);color:var(--red);border:1px solid rgba(255,48,96,.2); }
.dow-neu  { background:rgba(255,184,0,.08);color:var(--gold);border:1px solid rgba(255,184,0,.2); }

/* Animations */
@keyframes blink   { 0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.3} }
@keyframes spin    { to{transform:rotate(360deg)} }
@keyframes fadeUp  { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)} }
@keyframes glow    { 0%,100%{box-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(0,240,160,.2)}50%{box-shadow:0 0 50px rgba(0,240,160,.4)} }

/* scrollbar */
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px}
::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--bg)}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border);border-radius:4px}

/* ── CONFETTI ── */
.confetti-piece {
  position:fixed;width:10px;height:10px;
  border-radius:2px;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999;
  animation:confetti-fall linear forwards;
}
@keyframes confetti-fall {
  0%   { transform:translateY(-20px) rotate(0deg); opacity:1; }
  100% { transform:translateY(100vh) rotate(720deg); opacity:0; }
}

/* ── WIN RATE ── */
.wr-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:8px;padding:16px; }
.wr-cell {
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:12px;padding:14px 10px;text-align:center;
}
.wr-num  { font-family:var(--font);font-size:28px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;margin-bottom:4px; }
.wr-lbl  { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:2px; }
.wr-bar-track { height:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border-radius:999px;overflow:hidden;margin:12px 16px 0; }
.wr-bar-fill  { height:100%;border-radius:999px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--green),var(--blue));transition:width 1s ease; }

.outcome-btns { display:flex;gap:8px;padding:0 16px 16px; }
.outcome-btn {
  flex:1;padding:10px;border-radius:10px;border:none;
  font-family:var(--font);font-size:14px;font-weight:600;
  cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;letter-spacing:1px;
}
.btn-win  { background:rgba(0,240,160,.15);color:var(--green);border:1px solid rgba(0,240,160,.3); }
.btn-win:hover  { background:rgba(0,240,160,.25); }
.btn-lose { background:rgba(255,48,96,.1);color:var(--red);border:1px solid rgba(255,48,96,.2); }
.btn-lose:hover { background:rgba(255,48,96,.2); }
.btn-reset{ background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);color:var(--muted);border:1px solid var(--border); }
.btn-reset:hover{ color:var(--text); }

/* ── BOTTOM NAV ── */
.bottom-nav {
  position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:998;
  background:rgba(11,15,30,.92);
  backdrop-filter:blur(20px);
  border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-around;
  padding:10px 0 16px;
}
body.light .bottom-nav {
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.92);
}
.nav-item {
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:4px;
  cursor:pointer;padding:4px 16px;border-radius:12px;
  transition:all .2s;flex:1;
  border:none;background:none;
}
.nav-item:hover { background:rgba(0,240,160,.08); }
.nav-item.active .nav-icon { color:var(--green); }
.nav-item.active .nav-label { color:var(--green); }
.nav-icon { font-size:20px;line-height:1; }
.nav-label {
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;
  color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:1px;
}
/* Push content above nav */
main { padding-bottom: 100px; }

@media(max-width:600px){
  .strategy-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
  .levels-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
  .analysis-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .analysis-col:first-child{border-right:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
  .signal-big{font-size:36px;}
  .conf-num{font-size:34px;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="brand">
    <div class="brand-logo" style="padding:0;overflow:hidden;border-radius:50%;width:48px;height:48px;">
    <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center top;display:block;">
  </div>
    <div class="brand-name">
      <h1>G-TRADER</h1>
      <p>DOW · FVG · BOS/CHOCH · H&S</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="header-right">

    <div class="badge badge-live">
      <div class="badge-dot"></div>
      AI LIVE
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main>

  <!-- Strategy overview -->
  <div class="section-title">СТРАТЕГИ</div>
  <div class="strategy-grid">
    <div class="s-card">
      <div class="s-icon">📈</div>
      <div class="s-title">DOW THEORY</div>
      <div class="s-name">HH/HL · LH/LL</div>
    </div>
    <div class="s-card">
      <div class="s-icon">🔲</div>
      <div class="s-title">FVG</div>
      <div class="s-name">Fair Value Gap</div>
    </div>
    <div class="s-card">
      <div class="s-icon">💥</div>
      <div class="s-title">BOS / CHOCH</div>
      <div class="s-name">Structure Break</div>
    </div>
    <div class="s-card">
      <div class="s-icon">📐</div>
      <div class="s-title">H&S PATTERN</div>
      <div class="s-name">Inv H&S · H&S</div>
    </div>
  </div>



  <!-- Upload -->
  <div class="section-title">CHART ЗУРАГ</div>
  <div id="drop-zone">
    <div class="drop-inner" id="placeholder">
      <div class="drop-icon">📊</div>
      <div class="drop-title">Chart зураг оруулна уу</div>
      <div class="drop-sub">TradingView screenshot — drag & drop эсвэл дарна уу</div>
    </div>
    <img id="preview" style="display:none">
  </div>
  <input type="file" id="file-input" accept="image/*">

  <div class="btn-row" id="btn-row" style="display:none">
    <button class="btn-analyze" id="btn-analyze" onclick="analyze()">
      🔍 AI ШИНЖЛЭХ
    </button>
    <button class="btn-clear" onclick="clearAll()">✕</button>
  </div>

  <!-- API Key -->
  <div class="api-box" style="margin-bottom:12px">
    <label>ANTHROPIC API KEY</label>
    <input type="password" id="gemini-key" class="api-input" placeholder="sk-ant-api03-...">
    <p class="api-hint">🔑 console.anthropic.com → API Keys → Create Key</p>
  </div>

  <div class="error-box" id="error-box" style="display:none"></div>

  <div class="result" id="result" style="display:none"></div>

</main>

<script>
const SYSTEM_PROMPT = `You are G-Trader Pro, an expert Forex/Gold signal AI. Analyze charts using ALL FOUR methods simultaneously:

1. DOW THEORY: Identify trend via Higher Highs/Higher Lows (uptrend) or Lower Highs/Lower Lows (downtrend). Determine if trend is intact or breaking.

2. FVG (Fair Value Gap): Count bearish FVGs (downside gaps) and bullish FVGs (upside gaps). Multiple bearish FVGs = strong downtrend. First bullish FVG after downtrend = potential reversal.

3. BOS/CHOCH:
   - BOS (Break of Structure): price breaks previous swing high/low continuing trend
   - CHOCH (Change of Character): price breaks opposite swing, signaling trend reversal
   Identify which occurred recently.

4. H&S PATTERNS:
   - Inverse H&S after downtrend = BUY signal
   - H&S after uptrend = SELL signal

BUY SIGNAL: Dow downtrend → Multiple Bearish FVGs → CHOCH (reversal signal) → Bullish FVG forms → Inverse H&S completes
SELL SIGNAL: Dow uptrend → Multiple Bullish FVGs → CHOCH → Bearish FVG forms → H&S completes

Respond ONLY with this JSON, no markdown:
{
  "signal": "BUY or SELL or WAIT",
  "pair": "XAUUSD",
  "timeframe": "detected timeframe",
  "dow_trend": "BULLISH or BEARISH or SIDEWAYS",
  "dow_structure": "HH/HL or LH/LL or MIXED",
  "dow_intact": true,
  "fvg_bearish_count": 0,
  "fvg_bullish_count": 0,
  "fvg_signal": "bearish or bullish or neutral",
  "bos_detected": true,
  "choch_detected": true,
  "bos_choch_type": "BOS or CHOCH or NONE",
  "bos_choch_direction": "bullish or bearish or none",
